<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_261_r1l2">Erſamer lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . vns hat der erſam <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu ſand Lorencʒen </ab>
