<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l5">von 
<add><ab facs="#facs_261_line_1576664036202_7899">den </ab></add> Lewfften vnd gelegenheıt des <expan>Co<ex>n</ex>cılıu<ex>m</ex>s</expan> herab <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . Des wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l6"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ danken . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>lantman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> weıſe <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l7">vvıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der Römıſch vnd ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc künıg <expan>kürcʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_261_r1l8">gen Coſtencʒ <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> ſülle . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr </ab>
